3. Reaſons from the profite of loue.Thirdly, the commodities of this loue ſhould moue vs to the entertainement and performance of it.
For firſt,1. Commodity. by this loue our faith produceth thoſe good duties, which we owe to GOD. For Faith, is as an Hand Receiuing, but by loue we giue and beſtow, and without it wee can do no good workes well: Therefore the Apoſtle ſaith,Gal. 5. 6. that Faith worketh by loue: And as Saint Auſten ſpeaketh, Our life and all our conuerſation is named of our loue: Nec faciunt bonos vel malos mores, niſi boni vel mali ſint amores: Which being good or bad, makes our manners to be thereafter; ſuch as the loue is, ſuch is the life;
